rook.api.transport.simple

Class SimpleAnnounceTransport

  • java.lang.Object
    • rook.api.transport.simple.SimpleAnnounceTransport
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AnnounceTransport

    public class SimpleAnnounceTransport
extends Object
implements AnnounceTransport
    Generic implementation of an AnnounceTransport that provides logic to manage and dispatch messages to consumers. It uses a Publisher implementation to send events to the process's Router.
    Author:
    Eric Thill
